{"tid":104373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[自卑的毒撚]入黎講下自己有幾毒","createTime":"2017-02-02T05:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T19:31:02.000Z","uid":75870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"770587712d0512ae520386106385f9e4c40c47d4","tid":104373,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"小五開始做毒撚，已經比同班同學標籤做電車男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過年唔識講恭賀說話 收利是淨係敢講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連同輩親戚都無乜幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小巴會細細聲嗌落車 司機聽唔到就會好心急咁望住佢但唔敢再出聲 直至有人嗌落車先一齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識同人溝通 超驚deadair 轉話題快過保特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果就係更多deadair<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nfb 已經5年無轉過相 因為驚無人like<br />\n<br />\n連登開post都掙扎左好耐 因為驚無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎挑機"},{"pid":"325e530f254ceeff303614c889ddf3ff08bdfc78","tid":104373,"uid":65705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"比啲存在感你"},{"pid":"3b702065c6967f18efa66df13c5c55381164b6fb","tid":104373,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"差唔多毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由個樣毒出黎，人人都知我睇動漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cb6b133cbe190880a0cb9520e879c8c0dd6216","tid":104373,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比啲存在感你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687ca3dfb67e86905bd18c3fe98386f0ff62bcfb","tid":104373,"uid":75870,"like":0